    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BURN ENERGY, SEEK REVENGE.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ENERGY-SACRIFICE TECH AWAKENS THE POWER OF VENGEANCE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AS DEATH LOOMS, UNLEASH BERSERK.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAUGES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ENERGY</strong> ― DEPLETES OVER TIME OR WHEN DAMAGED, AND RECOVERS BY DEFEATING FOES OR GATHERING DATA CHIPS. LOSING ALL RESULTS IN DEFEAT.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ADRENALINE</strong> ― RISES AS YOU TAKE RISKS, AND CAN REACH ITS PEAK TO UNLEASH BERSERKER.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACTIONS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BLADE</strong> ― DELIVER A SPINNING SLASH THAT SWEEPS THROUGH FOES AS YOU ADVANCE.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KUNAI</strong> ― THROW PRECISELY AT A DISTANT FOE TO CHIP AWAY THEIR HEALTH.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ROLL</strong> ― QUICKLY DODGE FOE ATTACKS, BUT SOME ARE UNAVOIDABLE.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BERSERK</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >AWAKING THE POWER OF VENGEANCE PUTS YOU INTO A FOCUSED STATE, SLOWING DOWN TIME.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WHEN THE TIME COMES, YOUR CLONES WILL PAINFULLY SLASH THEIR TARGETS, BUT THE RECOIL WILL TEMPORARILY FREEZE THEM.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BURN ENERGY, SEEK REVENGE!</strong></p>",
